{"tid":1461852,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「全民換美金」入黎我教你0 風險賺8% 回報！","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:27:33.000Z","uid":285330,"like":7,"dislike":184,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"046412b31160a0d98513801721589de6a4ab2640","tid":1461852,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:27:17.000Z","msg":"你可能話：邊有咁大隻蛤乸隨街跳，屌我話比你聽，有！點解？關加密貨幣事！<br />\n<br />\n可能你只係識Bitcoin，但其實依家市面上已經有幾千種唔同既加密貨幣。而其中一類叫做「穩定貨幣(Stablecoin)，即係同法定貨幣 (Fiat) 掛勾，但底層係利用區塊鏈技術既加密貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n市面有d 加密貨幣初創係做借貸生意，即係如果你有1 粒Bitcoin 做抵押品，就可以問佢借5000 USD咁，而呢5000  USD 通常係用Stablecoin 放出黎 (e.g.: TUSD / PAXO / USDC)，到期就問客拎返本金+利息。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，咁關8% 回報咩事呢？你可以想像呢ｄ公司要借錢出街，即係都需要cap 水啦！所以好多呢類公司除左Credit Services 都有Earn Services，即係你放ｄ Stablecoin 入去就可以做定存賺利息，而目前市面上既利息係做到6-8%!<br />\n<br />\n呢類公司分別有：<br />\n<br />\nNexos <a href=\"https://nexo.io/?utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_campaign=upperfunnel&amp;utm_term=search&amp;utm_content=brand&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI__jDoO3-4wIVDqyWCh2mpATQEAAYASAAEgJxOfD_BwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnexo.io%2F%3Futm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dupperfunnel%26utm_term%3Dsearch%26utm_content%3Dbrand%26gclid%3DEAIaIQobChMI__jDoO3-4wIVDqyWCh2mpATQEAAYASAAEgJxOfD_BwE&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=4c9db48e\" target=\"_blank\">https://nexo.io/?utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_campaign=upperfunnel&amp;utm_term=search&amp;utm_content=brand&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI__jDoO3-4wIVDqyWCh2mpATQEAAYASAAEgJxOfD_BwE</a><br />\nCelsius Network <a href=\"https://celsius.network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcelsius.network%2F&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=10e7d69c\" target=\"_blank\">https://celsius.network/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://Crypto.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCrypto.com&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=3f4fd3f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Crypto.com</a> (Seems Earn not supported for HK Citizens) <a href=\"https://crypto.com/en/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrypto.com%2Fen%2Findex.html&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=8ec5364f\" target=\"_blank\">https://crypto.com/en/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n哇，好似好正咁wor，但我點匯錢入去呢ｄ公司到？<br />\n<br />\n答案：透過Stablecoin 既官方網站！佢地通常有提供用Wire Transfer 既方法，即係你可以由你既銀行帳戶直接匯款去Stablecoin 公司既戶口！通常需要1-2日既匯款時間同幾百蚊手續費（如果你用花旗匯款去美國可以免埋手續費）<br />\n<br />\nStablecoin 公司分別有：<br />\n<br />\nTSUD <a href=\"https://www.trusttoken.com/trueusd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trusttoken.com%2Ftrueusd&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=0b6f6d73\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.trusttoken.com/trueusd</a><br />\nPAXOs Standard <a href=\"https://www.paxos.com/pax/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paxos.com%2Fpax%2F&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=830a589c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.paxos.com/pax/</a><br />\nUSDC <a href=\"https://www.circle.com/en/usdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.circle.com%2Fen%2Fusdc&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=5c60621d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.circle.com/en/usdc</a><br />\n<br />\n好，所以要賺8% risk free interest 既流程分別就係：<br />\n<br />\n1.       去Nexos / Celsius Network / <a href=\"http://Crypto.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCrypto.com&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=3f4fd3f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Crypto.com</a> (任選其一) 註冊<br />\n2.       去 TSUD / PAXO / USDC (任選其一) 註冊<br />\n3.       係你既銀行將港元換做美元<br />\n4.       將美元匯去Stablecoin 既帳戶<br />\n5.       去Stablecoin 帳戶將美元轉成Stablecoin (1:1 匯率)<br />\n6.       將Stablecoin withdraw 去 Nexos / Celsius network / <a href=\"http://Crypto.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCrypto.com&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=3f4fd3f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Crypto.com</a><br />\n7.       做定存，賺8% 利息！<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n<br />\nQ: 哇屌你咁撚煩，費撚事搞。<br />\nA: 無風險賺8%，你唔做大把人做<br />\n<br />\nQ: 呢d 公司會唔會執笠架，我唔信真係無風險。<br />\nA: 你岩，其實係有counter-party risk。點衡量回報 (8%) 同風險，自行決定<br />\n<br />\nQ: 屌我唔撚信Bitcoin，係咪騙局黎架？<br />\nA: 家陣叫你用Stablecoin 唔係bitcoin，完全無volatility。而且個人意見，依家中美貿易戰＋香港局勢動盪，其實對Bitcoin 係大利好，個人好贊成買少少做對沖<br />\n<br />\n對唔住大家我唔得閒整埋圖文解說，有心既巴打可以試完補上！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ec0143e7a56fb2de7aa2d3ad2c30ef76d98132","tid":1461852,"uid":58335,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OReqtxs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOReqtxs.png&h=4f83398c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a86fbb5a7c7157209c18f28551cc1b41f336334","tid":1461852,"uid":55669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14ec0143e7a56fb2de7aa2d3ad2c30ef76d98132","tid":1461852,"uid":58335,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OReqtxs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOReqtxs.png&h=4f83398c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8517843dd2fa9a7efdeb891fae998b218b9469d1","tid":1461852,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"推～"},{"pid":"1a8502ee736a309a13d62f9d076e5f5ba87e267f","tid":1461852,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"做乜咁多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/